# 1. 
setwd("/Users/yeguo/Desktop/GB/MAGdb_plot_V2/Figure_5/data/")
data <- read.csv("tree_rawdata.csv", header = TRUE, stringsAsFactors = FALSE)

# class
raw_data <- data %>%
  count(Bin, p) %>%
  pivot_wider(
    names_from = Bin,
    values_from = n,
    values_fill = 0
  ) %>%
  column_to_rownames("p")

# 
all_meta <- read.csv("metadata.csv", header = TRUE, stringsAsFactors = FALSE)
filter_meta <- all_meta %>%
  filter(Run_accession %in% colnames(raw_data)) %>%
  distinct(Run_accession, .keep_all = TRUE) %>%
  arrange(match(Run_accession, colnames(raw_data)))  # 

rownames(filter_meta) <- filter_meta$Run_accession
filter_meta <- sample_data(filter_meta)

# 
stopifnot(identical(colnames(raw_data), rownames(filter_meta)))

tax_table <- row.names(raw_data)

# write.csv(tax_table, "tax_table.csv", row.names = FALSE) # 

# 2. phyloseq
otu2tax <- read.csv("tax_table.csv", row.names = 1)
ps <- phyloseq(
  sample_data(filter_meta),
  otu_table(as.matrix(raw_data), taxa_are_rows = TRUE),
  tax_table(as.matrix(otu2tax))
)

rank_names(ps)

library(ggrepel)  # 
library(dplyr)
library(ggrepel)

# 1. category
node$category <- factor(node$category,
                        levels = c("animal", "Environment", "Clinical"),
                        labels = c("Animal", "Environment", "Clinical"))  # 

edge$category <- factor(edge$category,
                        levels = c("animal", "Environment", "Clinical"),
                        labels = c("Animal", "Environment", "Clinical"))

# 
degree_threshold <- 5  # 


# 2. 
high_degree_nodes <- node %>%
  filter(igraph.degree > degree_threshold)

# 3. 
p <- ggplot() + 
  # 
  geom_segment(
    aes(x = X1, y = Y1, xend = X2, yend = Y2, color = cor),
    data = edge, 
    linewidth = 1.5,
    alpha = 0.5
  ) +
  # 
  geom_point(
    aes(X1, X2, fill = phylum, size = igraph.degree),
    data = node,
    shape = 21,
    color = "gray40"
  ) +
  # 
  geom_text_repel(
    aes(X1, X2, label = elements),
    data = high_degree_nodes,
    size = 3,
    color = "black",
    box.padding = 0.5,
    max.overlaps = 10,
    min.segment.length = 2
  ) +
  # 
  facet_wrap(
    ~category,
    nrow = 1,
    scales = "free"  #  "fixed" 
  ) +
  # 
  scale_colour_manual(values = c("#6D98B5", "#D48852")) +
  scale_size(range = c(1, 10), name = "Degree") +
  scale_x_continuous(breaks = NULL) +
  scale_y_continuous(breaks = NULL) +
  theme(
    panel.background = element_blank(),
    legend.title = element_text(size = 16),  # 
    legend.text = element_text(size = 14),    # 
    plot.title = element_text(hjust = 0.5),
    axis.title = element_blank(),
    legend.background = element_rect(colour = NA),
    panel.grid = element_blank(),
    strip.text = element_text(size = 14, face = "bold")  # 
  ) +
  guides(fill = "none")

print(p)
